EPS = 0.0001
partitionFrameThk = 0.03

!!!4 - Left End Partition !!!2 - Side Partition / Side 1 !!!1 - Front Partition !!!3 - Right End Partition / Side 2
bEndPartitions1 = 0 bSidePartitions = (gs_partitionType_m = 2 or gs_partitionType_m = 4 or gs_partitionType_m = 6 or gs_partitionType_m = 7) bFrontPartitions = (gs_partitionType_m = 1 or gs_partitionType_m = 4 or gs_partitionType_m = 5 or gs_partitionType_m = 7) bEndPartitions2 = (gs_partitionType_m = 3 or gs_partitionType_m = 5 or gs_partitionType_m = 6 or gs_partitionType_m = 7)
!!!!! Existing Partitions dim existPartition[4] existPartition[4] = 0 existPartition[2] = bSidePartitions existPartition[1] = bFrontPartitions existPartition[3] = bEndPartitions2
!!!!! Desk Partition Length dim partLength[4] partLength[4] = 0 partLength[2] = gs_partitionLength_side1 partLength[1] = gs_partitionLength_front partLength[3] = gs_partitionLength_side2
!!!!! Desk Partition Distance dim partPos[4][2] partPos[4][1] = 0 partPos[2][1] = 0 partPos[1][1] = a / 2 partPos[3][1] = a
partPos[4][2] = 0 partPos[2][2] = b / 2 partPos[1][2] = 0 partPos[3][2] = b / 2
!!!!! Desk Partition Cutting xPosFrontPartLeftSide = partPos[1][1] + gs_partitionPos_front[1][1] - partLength[1] / 2 yPosFrontPartLeftSide = partPos[1][2] + gs_partitionPos_front[1][2] xPosFrontPartRightSide = partPos[1][1] + gs_partitionPos_front[1][1] + partLength[1] / 2 yPosFrontPartRightSide = partPos[1][2] + gs_partitionPos_front[1][2]

partCornerCutFront1 = (ABS(xPosFrontPartLeftSide - xPosSide1PartLowerSide) < EPS and ABS(yPosFrontPartLeftSide - yPosSide1PartLowerSide) < EPS) and bSidePartitions and bFrontPartitions partCornerCutFront2 = (ABS(xPosFrontPartRightSide - xPosSide2PartLowerSide) < EPS and ABS(yPosFrontPartRightSide - yPosSide2PartLowerSide) < EPS) and bEndPartitions2 and bFrontPartitions

bShowPartitionParams = bFrontPartitions or\ bSidePartitions or\ bEndPartitions1 or\ bEndPartitions2 bShowCabParams = gs_officeCab_m > OFFICECAB_NONE bShowCommonCabParams = bShowCabParams
